snippet.title: Deducto 2 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Deducto 2 on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2119590/Deducto_2/

A fun sus-like game where you backstab your co-workers and get mad at your co-workers for backstabbing you. (up to 10 players)
